WEBVTT

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:00.520
laughs,

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:03.136
calls me a name,

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:04.640
or takes a photograph of me.

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:07.389
This happens almost every day.

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:11.616
With the rise of social media,
it has given me an opportunity

00:06:11.640 --> 00:06:15.600
and a platform to have a voice
as a blogger and as an activist,

00:06:16.440 --> 00:06:18.736
but it has also made me nervous

00:06:18.760 --> 00:06:20.856
that I might become a meme

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:22.440
or a viral sensation,

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:24.800
all without my consent.

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:28.936
So let's take a moment right now

00:06:28.960 --> 00:06:30.560
to make something very clear.